{"title":"","date":"2021-01-04T10:22:52.098Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jan 4, 2021","L":"01/04/2021","MM-DD":"01-04"},"updated":"2021-01-04T10:22:52.098Z","content":"<h1 id=\"心理咨询系统说明文档\">心理咨询系统说明文档<a title=\"#心理咨询系统说明文档\" href=\"#心理咨询系统说明文档\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"名词解释与对照\">名词解释与对照<a title=\"#名词解释与对照\" href=\"#名词解释与对照\"></a></h2>\n<div class=\"φcy\"><div class=\"φda\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">类别</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">中文</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">英文</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">释义</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">人物</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">教师</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">teacher</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">咨询师</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">consultant</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">助管</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">asistant</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">学生</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">student</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">时间</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">学期</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">semester</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">教学周</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">week</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">星期几</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">dayOfWeek</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">第几节课</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">lesson</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">开始时间</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">begin</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">结束时间</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">end</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">信息</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">学号/工号</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">id</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">性别</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">gender</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">权限</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">auth</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">学院</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">ins</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">专业</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">majer</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">班级</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">class</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\"></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div><h2 id=\"database-schema\">DataBase Schema<a title=\"#database-schema\" href=\"#database-schema\"></a></h2>\n<p>数据库分为两大部分：用户系统和咨询事件</p>\n<p>由于用户系统较为复杂，我们先讲咨询事件</p>\n<h3 id=\"consultation\">Consultation<a title=\"#consultation\" href=\"#consultation\"></a></h3>\n<p>每一次咨询为一个 consultation, 会与四个人物相链接</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">consultation: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 时间相关字段</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">Date</span>: <span class=\"string\">\"2020-08-11\"</span>, <span class=\"comment\">// Date</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    semester: <span class=\"string\">\"2020-2021-1\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    week: <span class=\"number\">1</span>, <span class=\"comment\">// integer, [1-16]</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    dayOfWeek: <span class=\"number\">1</span>, <span class=\"comment\">// integer, [1-7],</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    lesson: <span class=\"number\">1</span>, <span class=\"comment\">// integer, [1-6],</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    begin: <span class=\"string\">\"7:30\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    end: <span class=\"string\">\"9:00\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 人物相关字段</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    teacher: &#123; <span class=\"string\">\"ObjectId\"</span> &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    consultant: &#123; <span class=\"string\">\"ObjectId\"</span> &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    asistant: &#123; <span class=\"string\">\"ObjectId\"</span> &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    student: &#123; <span class=\"string\">\"ObjectId\"</span> &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 地点相关字段</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    classroom: <span class=\"string\">\"102\"</span>, <span class=\"comment\">// String</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 咨询内容</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    note: <span class=\"string\">\"本次咨询的相关记录, 也可以存储图片\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"user-system\">User System<a title=\"#user-system\" href=\"#user-system\"></a></h3>\n<p>用户分为四类：教师(teacher)，咨询师(consultant)，助管(asistant)，学生(student)</p>\n<p>这些用户有一些公共的属性被单独提出来，存在userInfo字段中</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight js\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 用户的公用属性</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">userInfo: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    id: <span class=\"string\">\"41724241\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    name: <span class=\"string\">\"Vincente\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    gender: <span class=\"number\">1</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    upcoming: [&#123; <span class=\"string\">\"ObjectId\"</span> &#125;], <span class=\"comment\">// 预约的咨询</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    history: [&#123; <span class=\"string\">\"ObjectId\"</span> &#125;] <span class=\"comment\">// 进行过的咨询</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 教师</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">teacher: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    userInfo: &#123; <span class=\"string\">\"ObjectId\"</span> &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    intro: <span class=\"string\">\"心理咨询中心负责人\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    auth: [<span class=\"string\">\"\"</span>,<span class=\"string\">\"\"</span>,<span class=\"string\">\"\"</span>,<span class=\"string\">\"\"</span>],</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 咨询师</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">consultant: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    userInfo: &#123; <span class=\"string\">\"ObjectId\"</span> &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    intro: <span class=\"string\">\"国家二级心理咨询师，擅长时间管理\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 助管</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">asistant: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    userInfo: &#123; <span class=\"string\">\"ObjectId\"</span> &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 同学</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">student: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    userInfo: &#123; <span class=\"string\">\"ObjectId\"</span> &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    ins: <span class=\"string\">\"计算机与通信工程学院\"</span>, <span class=\"comment\">// string/integer</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    majer: <span class=\"string\">\"物联网工程\"</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    class: \"物联171\",</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","link":"fit/README","comments":true,"plink":"https://blog.vincenteliang.cn/fit/README/","toc":[{"id":"心理咨询系统说明文档","title":"心理咨询系统说明文档","index":"1","children":[{"id":"名词解释与对照","title":"名词解释与对照","index":"1.1"},{"id":"database-schema","title":"DataBase Schema","index":"1.2","children":[{"id":"consultation","title":"Consultation","index":"1.2.1"},{"id":"user-system","title":"User System","index":"1.2.2"}]}]}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"Vincente Liang","link":"<a href=\"https://blog.vincenteliang.cn/fit/README/\" title=\"undefined\">https://blog.vincenteliang.cn/fit/README/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"January 4, 2021","updated":"January 4, 2021"}}